OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA small chance of some patchy
OL,6,Flow cloud along the coast at first,
OL,7,Fquickly clearing to leave a dry day
OL,8,Fwith plenty of sunshine. Feeling hot
OL,9,Faway from the coast. Blustery coastal
OL,10,Fwinds expected.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry, with late
OL,13,Fevening sunshine. Remaining breezy
OL,14,Falong the coast. Some showers possible
OL,15,Fin the early hours of Thursday,
OL,16,Fparticularly in the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
