OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA fine day, with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine. Brisk southeasterly winds
OL,7,Fexpected, with some strong gusts along
OL,8,Fthe coast. Isolated showers possible
OL,9,Fin the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry but
OL,12,Fa little cooler on Friday. A band of
OL,13,Fpatchy rain moving in late on
OL,14,FSaturday, perhaps heavy and persistent
OL,15,Fovernight. Unsettled with showers
OL,16,Fpossible on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
